<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="plone">

<head>
    <metal:noborder fill-slot="top_slot"
                 tal:define="dummy python:request.set('disable_border',1)" />
</head>

<body>
<div metal:fill-slot="main">
  <div tal:condition="view/is_zippable">
    <p>
      This feature will create a compressed zip file of all content within this folder and its subfolders.
    </p>
    <p>
      This process may be slow for large folders, and will fail for very large folders.  Please contact <a href="mailto:portal.administration@imsweb.com">portal.administration@imsweb.com</a> for help
    </p>

    <a tal:attributes="href string:${here/absolute_url}/@@zipconfirm">
      <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-download-alt"></i>
      Download
    </a>
    <small>(pre-zipped estimated size: <span tal:content="view/size_estimate" />)</small>
  </div>
  <div tal:condition="not:view/is_zippable">
    <p>
      Sorry, this folder exceeds the allowed size for zip files. Please try zipping subfolders individually or
      contact <a href="mailto:portal.administration@imsweb.com">portal.administration@imsweb.com</a> for help.
    </p>

    <p>(pre-zipped estimated size: <span tal:content="view/size_estimate" />)</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>